        <title>阿里云 MCP Server 开箱即用！</title>
        <link>https://ai.programnotes.cn/p/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91-mcp-server-%E5%BC%80%E7%AE%B1%E5%8D%B3%E7%94%A8/</link>
